@_tomcc
Hey people, MCPE worlds in 0.9 can absolutely be infinite! 10k by 10k is just the default world size but you can change that.
嘿，大家！版本0.9 MCPE的世界可以是无限的！10k只是世界默认的大小，但你可以改变这一点。

@_tomcc
Actually, as we're short on time, we might add the limit in 0.9.1 and for the time being you have to live with endless worlds :P
事实上，正如我们在短的时间，我们可能会在 0.9.1 中添加“极限模式”，暂且你不得不忍受无尽世界 :P

@_tomcc
I've done a lot of bug-hunting this week, finally the game feels more like stable! Proof: relatively bug-free savanna
我这个星期修复了很多很多的BUG，终于在游戏中给人的感觉更像稳定的！一张证明：无bug的热带草原

@_tomcc
Please disregard the flying savanna tree, the situation is under control.
请忽略浮空的热带草原树，情况已受到控制。

@_tomcc
On the other hand, now MCPE actually generates worlds without any lighting artifact, the new 3x3 feature engine is a neat improvement.
另一方面，现在的MCPE实际上会生成世界无需任何照明工件，新的3x3特征引擎是一个整齐的改善。

